      "published_date": "2022-06-28T00:00:00.000Z",
      "text": "Working together to responsibly and economically SouthwestPowerPool SPPorg southwest\n-power-pool keep the lights on today and in the future.\nWorking together to responsibly and economically SouthwestPowerPool SPPorg southwest-power-pool keep the lights on today and in the future. 2\nPARTICIPATION MODELS & \nMITIGATION\nSPP MARKETS\n6/28/2022\n3\nPARTICIPATION MODEL\n4\nWHO CAN PARTICIPATE IN MARKETS+?\nAn entity that:\n• Generates\n• Transmits\n• Distributes\n• Purchases or Sells \nElectricity within, into, out of \nor through the Markets+ \nFootprint.\nParticipation includes:\n• Wholesale Energy \nSettlement with SPP\n• Asset Registration and \nParticipation\n• Market Participant \nObligations necessary for \neffective and efficient market\n• Metering, credit, data \nrequirements, etc.\n5\nRESOURCE\nPARTICIPATION MODEL\n6\nDEMAND \nRESPONSE\nEXTERNAL TO \nSPP BA\nGENERATION\nVARIABLE \nENERGY\nENERGY \nSTORAGE\nRESOURCE ASSET REGISTRATION TYPES\nDemand response Resources that can physically reduce or shift their \nelectricity",
